cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for 3D human pose estimation from a single image. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel approach using distance matrix regression, which involves training a neural network, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves formulating the problem as a regression task, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves handling missing observations, which falls under cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper involves evaluating the approach on datasets, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia).
